        <Summary>An HTML Help viewer for Unix/Linux</Summary>
        <Description>ChmSee is an HTML Help viewer for Unix/Linux. It is based on CHMLIB and use Gtk+ as frontend toolkit. Because of using gecko as HTML rendering engine, ChmSee can support rich features of modern HTML page, such as CSS and JavaScript.</Description>
